# 💡 Skill Swap Platform

A collaborative platform where users can exchange skills by offering what they know and requesting what they want to learn. This creates a community-driven learning environment that eliminates the need for financial transactions and promotes mutual growth.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🌐 User-friendly interface for skill matching
- 🔍 Search and filter users by skills or availability
- 🔁 Skill offered ↔ Skill wanted matching
- 📩 Skill swap request system
- 👤 Profile display with ratings and avatars

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

| Layer            | Tech Used                       |
|------------------|----------------------------------|
| Frontend         | HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React     |
| Styling          | Custom CSS, Bootstrap / Tailwind |
| Backend (future) | Node.js / Express or JSP/Servlet |
| Version Control  | Git & GitHub                     |

